{"id": 2037, "genre": 1001, "title": "购买护肤品 or 化妆品的时候，你都讲究些什么？", "description": "或者说，它们具备的哪些属性会让你买前三思？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2961, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171129152430rTbJPhci0VU2AtW1.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-01T03:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 252160, "content": "贵的一般确实好用，有些便宜的效果也不一定逊色。比如一些小众国货。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66079}, {"id": 252161, "content": "预算\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125060}, {"id": 252417, "content": "适不适合，性价比，最关键一点买不买得起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 252162, "content": "查查评价和功效", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617245}, {"id": 252418, "content": "无香精无酒精无添加", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202261}, {"id": 252163, "content": "化妆宝典，小红书种草推荐的好用的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200423}, {"id": 252164, "content": "性价比高", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197921}, {"id": 253957, "content": "成分/颜值/价位/预算", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211534}, {"id": 252166, "content": "官方发布的成分效果和wb等渠道的测评。常用品牌的新品会争取拿多点小样试用", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009956}, {"id": 252422, "content": "这个产品是否符合国家生产要求", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202488}, {"id": 252423, "content": "安全，方便，好用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071072}, {"id": 252168, "content": "是不是正品？有没有效果？", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 252169, "content": "寻求植物护肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981884}, {"id": 252170, "content": "既买得起又适合我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200442}, {"id": 252171, "content": "香的 买～ 好看的 买～ 有效果 继续回购", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198284}, {"id": 252427, "content": "作为一个护肤狂人！我想说每次买护肤品都会先看成分表！大家都很喜欢种草爆款的护肤品。但是要第一时间想一想你是什么肤质？价格？这些你都要考虑到。最近给大家一个非常实用的app~叫做美丽修行！特别好用。只要把你想知道的护肤品的名字打上去它就会显示出它里面含有的成分！不会作假！很放心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202532}, {"id": 327179, "content": "价格 对我是不是真的必要（不能为了一时冲动消费 ）适不适合我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581828}, {"id": 252428, "content": "品牌，成分，香精，酒精", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202566}, {"id": 252173, "content": "购买渠道 是否是正品", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186143}, {"id": 252174, "content": "适合什么皮啊 会不会起痘", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066613}, {"id": 338703, "content": "和目前的室内风格，衣着风格是否相符", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 252431, "content": "是否适合自己的肤质", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049413}, {"id": 252176, "content": "会不会搓泥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152118}, {"id": 252177, "content": "适不适合自己 别人的反馈测评 效果好不好 以及自己是否需要", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200450}, {"id": 252433, "content": "适不适合自己的皮肤和风格", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202605}, {"id": 252178, "content": "是否安全，有效成分是什么，以及它的作用机理。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180053}, {"id": 252179, "content": "过不过敏", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194650}, {"id": 252435, "content": "真货还是假货 哪里可以买到真货", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153798}, {"id": 252181, "content": "在知道自己需求的情况下，往贵了买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200469}, {"id": 252182, "content": "时效性和性价比", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 252438, "content": "包装。。这个是重点 还有会不会过敏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198997}, {"id": 255510, "content": "味道啊，我是嗅觉动物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219037}, {"id": 252183, "content": "价格 产地", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088168}, {"id": 251672, "content": "不倾向于买连锁店自己品牌的产品，觉得不够专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 252184, "content": "适合自己的最重要。不要被乱七八糟推荐迷惑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 252440, "content": "我有钱吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123244}, {"id": 283673, "content": "1.大牌（心里感觉相对放心）\n2.是否适合自己（干皮油皮）\n3.效果如何（是否会让自己的皮肤或者其他好一些）\n4.哪里买靠谱（一般专柜）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354055}, {"id": 251673, "content": "看到名字很像外国货的陌生品牌，会先查查到底是哪里的品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 252185, "content": "包装精美程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166957}, {"id": 251674, "content": "对最近听到次数太多的品牌和产品保持警惕，可能都是软文或广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 252187, "content": "首先是会不会过敏 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171773}, {"id": 252443, "content": "性价比怎么样，价格和成分等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866147}, {"id": 252188, "content": "这些东西好吗？我自己喜欢吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192996}, {"id": 253212, "content": "知名品牌、看重纯天然成分，少含酒精等有伤皮肤的成分。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206776}, {"id": 252189, "content": "同样肤质的使用感受、价格以及效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178477}, {"id": 252445, "content": "自己喜欢的，而且适合自己风格的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135886}, {"id": 252190, "content": "功效和品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586174}, {"id": 252446, "content": "对皮肤伤害有多大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953514}, {"id": 252191, "content": "价格好，包装精致", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927399}, {"id": 252192, "content": "我一般看功效，是不是美白淡斑，产地也很重要，还有就是朋友的安利也可以。化妆品完全不知道怎么买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200448}]}